Nyamira county MCAs are concerned over a move my unknown people to vandalise street lights in various markets including Kemera, Kebirigo and Magombo. The vandals made any with solar panels, batteries and bulbs, affecting more than 20 lights. Bonyamatuta MCA Robinson Mocheche called the move as primitive and backward, saying a lot had been invested in the project to provide security. They called for investigation into the matter so as to bring the culprits to book.    